c: 5
v: 96
t: Tumharay liye dariya ka shikar pakrna aur iss ka khana halal kiya gaya hai. Tumharay faeeday kay wastay aur musafiron kay wastay aur khushki ka shikar pakarna tumharay liye haram kiya gaya hai jab tak tum halat-e-ehraam mein raho aur Allah Taalaa say daro jiss kay pass jama kiye jao gay